nd respect that. We're not going to reward that by turning off EQ in order to get everyone to play EQII.<hr height=1 noshade id=quote></BLOCKQUOTE id=quote></font id=quote><font face="Verdana" size=2 id=quote></P><P>Better?</P><P> </font></td>
